{
  "page": "Song of the Sea: How the Lands Were Severed",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Song of the Sea: How the Lands Were Severed</b></i> is a book written by Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Cassander\" title=\"Cassander\">Cassander</a>. In the book, Cassander argues that the <a href=\"/index.php/Breaking\" title=\"Breaking\">Breaking</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Arm_of_Dorne\" title=\"Arm of Dorne\">Arm of Dorne</a> was not shattered by the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Greenseer\" title=\"Greenseer\">greenseers</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Hammer_of_the_Waters\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Hammer of the Waters\">Hammer of the Waters</a>, but rather covered by the <b>Song of the Sea</b>, a slow rising of the oceans over centuries, caused by a series of long, hot summers and short, warm winters that melted the ice in the frozen lands north of the <a href=\"/index.php/Shivering_Sea\" title=\"Shivering Sea\">Shivering Sea</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_breaking.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_breaking.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Song_of_the_Sea:_How_the_Lands_Were_Severed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_breaking.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_breaking.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne: The Breaking.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404134642\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.015 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.016 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 99/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8550/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 411/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 118/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 596/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    8.786      1 -total\n 73.33%    6.443      1 Template:Ref\n 45.52%    3.999      1 Template:Ref/core\n 25.00%    2.196      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:20826-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404134642 and revision id 238721\n -->\n",
